text: Haliotis thailandis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Haliotidae, the abalones. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species has been found in the Andaman Sea and the seas around the Philippines OBIS : Haliotis thailandis ==References== Haliotis thailandis, apical view ==External links== thailandis Category:Gastropods described in 2001
title: Haliotis thailandis
